{"type": "root", "attrs": {"icon": "DOP/rbdglueobject", "parent": "rigidbodies"}, "body": [{"level": 0, "type": "title", "indent": 0, "text": ["RBD Glued Objects"], "extent": [47, 69]}, {"type": "summary", "indent": 0, "text": ["Creates a number of rigid bodies from SOP geometry and glues them together."], "extent": [69, 153]}, {"level": 2, "id": null, "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["Overview"], "extent": [153, 168], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["The ", {"scheme": "Shelf", "value": "rbdglueobject", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/shelf/rbdglueobject"}, " tool is useful for shattering pre-fractured geometry.\nIt creates multiple rigid bodies in the DOP simulation in the same manner as the ", {"scheme": "Shelf", "value": "rbdobjects", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/shelf/rbdobjects"}, " tool, but also creates a ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/constraintnetwork", "type": "link", "text": ["constraint network"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/constraintnetwork"}, " to glue together nearby pieces."], "extent": [168, 455]}, {"type": "tip_group", "body": [{"type": "tip", "indent": 0, "role": "item", "extent": [455, 460], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["To remove the name prefix, you can disable or remove the ", {"type": "code", "text": ["add_dop_object_name_prefix"]}, " node in the SOP network."], "extent": [460, 580]}], "container": true}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}]}, {"level": 2, "id": null, "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["Glue vs other constraint types"], "extent": [580, 617], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["Glue is very different than the other constraint types that the Bullet solver supports. Objects that are glued together are simulated together as a single object, as opposed to something like a pin constraint where the objects are simulated separately but a constraint tries to keep the anchor points at the same position/orientation. This means that the positions of the anchor points don\u2019t actually matter for glue, aside from visualization purposes."], "extent": [617, 1072]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["The current position of an anchor point is computed based on the initial position and the object\u2019s (rigid) transform. Deformation is not taken into account since anchor points are not, for example, attached to a particular point number in the object\u2019s geometry. You may want to update the constraint network\u2019s point positions on each frame for objects that are inactive and deforming. For glue though, that only affects visualization."], "extent": [1072, 1508]}]}, {"level": 2, "id": "includeme", "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["Using RBD Glued Objects"], "extent": [1508, 1550], "body": [{"type": "ord_group", "body": [{"blevel": 6, "type": "ord", "indent": 4, "text": ["Select the geometry to convert to RBD objects."], "extent": [1550, 1605]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "ord", "indent": 4, "text": ["If necessary, define the pieces to be fractured. For example, using the ", {"scheme": "Shelf", "value": "shatter", "type": "link", "text": ["Shatter tool"], "fullpath": "/shelf/shatter"}, "."], "extent": [1605, 1714]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "ord", "indent": 4, "text": ["Select the object and click the ", {"scheme": "Icon", "value": "DOP/rbdglueobject", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/shelf/DOP/rbdglueobject"}, {"scheme": "Shelf", "value": "rbdglueobject", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/shelf/rbdglueobject"}, " tool on the ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Rigid Bodies"]}, " tab."], "extent": [1714, 1833]}], "container": true}, {"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": [{"scheme": "Image", "value": "/images/shelf/rbd_fracture_object_before.jpg", "type": "img", "text": ""}, "  ", {"scheme": "Image", "value": "/images/shelf/rbd_glue_object_after.jpg", "type": "img", "text": ""}], "extent": [1833, 1940]}]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["For specific parameter help see the ", {"scheme": "Icon", "value": "DOP/rbdpackedobject", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/shelf/DOP/rbdpackedobject"}, {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/rbdpackedobject", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/rbdpackedobject"}, " help."], "extent": [1940, 2036]}, {"level": 2, "id": null, "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["Switching to the dynamics level"], "extent": [2036, 2074], "body": [{"type": "ord_group", "body": [{"blevel": 2, "type": "ord", "indent": 0, "text": ["Click the ", {"scheme": "Icon", "value": "TOOLS/select_dynamics", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/shelf/TOOLS/select_dynamics"}, "Dynamics Select Mode button on the ", {"scheme": null, "value": "/basics/select", "type": "link", "text": ["selector and handle controls toolbar"], "fullpath": "/basics/select"}, "."], "extent": [2074, 2206]}, {"blevel": 2, "type": "ord", "indent": 0, "text": ["Click ", {"keys": ["LMB"], "type": "keys", "text": null}, " the RBD glue object in the ", {"scheme": null, "value": "/ref/views/3dview", "type": "link", "text": ["scene view"], "fullpath": "/ref/views/3dview"}, "."], "extent": [2206, 2282]}], "container": true}]}, {"level": 1, "id": "related", "container": true, "type": "related_section", "indent": 0, "role": "section", "extent": [2282, 2291], "body": [{"type": "bullet_group", "body": [{"blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Shelf", "value": "rbdobjects", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/shelf/rbdobjects"}], "extent": [2291, 2313]}, {"blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/rbdpackedobject", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/rbdpackedobject"}], "extent": [2313, 2342]}, {"blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/constraintnetwork", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/constraintnetwork"}], "extent": [2342, 2373]}, {"blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/glueconrel", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/glueconrel"}], "extent": [2373, 2397]}], "container": true}], "text": "Related"}], "title": ["RBD Glued Objects"], "summary": ["Creates a number of rigid bodies from SOP geometry and glues them together."]}